    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What would you do if you were trapped in a dimension of seemingly endless rooms that went on for eternity? Based on the backrooms lore, this first person, walking simulator will take you on a 2 hour eerie adventure through a place that only exists in our nightmares. &quot;The Backrooms: Forsaken&quot; takes this concept one step further by introducing a companion character and full story to raise the stakes. If you're looking for a casual game this spooky season, and are good at mazes then &quot;The Backrooms: Forsaken&quot; is for you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What to expect:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-First person point of view</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Eerie situations and scary moments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Single player campaign</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-About 2 hours of gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Maze and Puzzle solving</p>",
